  "text": "Alternatively treatment may have been delayed because interferon-α (IFN-α) has major psychiatric side effects and PWID often have psychiatric comorbidities [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . But when they were treated, these persons had the second-highest virologic response. This finding is in line with publications that showed comparable treatment success in PWID and in people who do not inject drugs [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] .",
